    public class C_RodentGerbil
extends C_RodentFossorial
implements I_ConstantGerbil
    Case study on Gerbillus nigeriae: gerbils choose food, partners or shelter depending on their energetic state and their perceived environment.
    Author:
    Moussa Sall, 2015, rev. 2016, JLF 04.2017, JLF&MS 01.2018, JLF 07.218
